Dia. 01 White is Satisfied?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White plays the hane at 1 and after Black answers with 2 White can easily live with 3.
\par Some people might think this problem was too easy.
\par
\par If the sequence is played liked this, Black has to play at 4 and make bik. This would be a very big success for White.
\par However this variation is \cf1\b fake\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
