[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After White's hane at \'a1\'e2, Black doesn't block directly but plays the \cf1\b diagonal attachment\cf0\b0  at 1. This is a vital point.
